        <h4>The Brief</h4>
        <p>Synergraphics Ltd needed a redesign of their site which was another home made site. They already had their colour scheme and graphics in place, the just wanted the site modernised and made responsive.</p>
        <br>
        <div class="line"></div>
        <br>
        <h4>The Process</h4>
        <p>With the client I created wireframes for each page and used the Bootstrap framework in order to make a responsive site.  The slider is done using CSS3 only to make it lighter and the contact form is using PHP.</p>
        <br>
        <div class="line"></div>
        <br>
        <h4>The Outcome</h4>
        <p>This is a responsive and clean looking site and I would like to thank Synergraphics for giving me the opportunity to work with them.</p>
